ic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/39a94e1923134a93fd1b8cd8f7067b4c.poster.avif?t=1738065410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/39a94e1923134a93fd1b8cd8f7067b4c.webm?t=1738065410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/39a94e1923134a93fd1b8cd8f7067b4c.mp4?t=1738065410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/a28e3f70f60c98a512a30085d53c0c8b.poster.avif?t=1738065410\" width=616 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/a28e3f70f60c98a512a30085d53c0c8b.webm?t=1738065410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/a28e3f70f60c98a512a30085d53c0c8b.mp4?t=1738065410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>DEATHRUN TV brings streamers and their audience together with crazy & addictive Twitch integrations allowing viewers to type various crazy commands in chat in order to trigger in-game events. Will they help you by making you extra huge? Or will they lead you to your doom by unleashing a horde of monsters on you?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/797de135472c032bb52b763596fb6e18.poster.avif?t=1738065410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/797de135472c032bb52b763596fb6e18.webm?t=1738065410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591690/extras/797de135472c032bb52